{"tid":1229394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國戰線] 麻煩花你一分鐘，入一入黎，請求幫忙。反送中集會","createTime":"2019-06-16T02:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:10:49.000Z","uid":251298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be092809bdc7fb5614b3b8493ceb50cc935805f6","tid":1229394,"uid":251298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"由於我剛剛得知我所在既地方都有反送中集會<br />\n本人都想略盡棉力<br />\n但可惜既係我英語能力好差<br />\n唔識佢點樣話俾澳洲人知香港的情況以及我想大大力宣揚香港警察哋。<br />\n有無巴打絲打可以幫忙，整幾張宣傳單張，比我可以印出黎，我一陣就出發去印同派。<br />\n求巴打絲打幫忙！求你，祝你地一世平安<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋定高牆，我永遠站在雞蛋，站在抗爭這既一方，希望大家都站在雞蛋一方。一眾勇士義士，我愛你們，天祐你們。<br />\n<br />\n極權既統治，不公既政策，成就今日既勇士義士<br />\n我向一眾勇士義士致以最崇高既敬意，多謝你，多謝你堅持守護自己既香港🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n特別祝各位受傷勇士義士，早日安全康復&bull;"},{"pid":"597ecc587f1779906404ee2cfcff80183685f552","tid":1229394,"uid":260914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"有人譯左英文版PDF<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hn4lap6XW7IwZjx3VfQYQowWnfcxltrV/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1hn4lap6XW7IwZjx3VfQYQowWnfcxltrV%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=be0bc851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hn4lap6XW7IwZjx3VfQYQowWnfcxltrV/view?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"886f2ad506733fc0ad05261186475fbebe7690ea","tid":1229394,"uid":251298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597ecc587f1779906404ee2cfcff80183685f552","tid":1229394,"uid":260914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"有人譯左英文版PDF<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hn4lap6XW7IwZjx3VfQYQowWnfcxltrV/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1hn4lap6XW7IwZjx3VfQYQowWnfcxltrV%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=be0bc851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.goog